---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Shader from "../components/Shader.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <div
    class="min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-center font-mono text-sm w-full max-w-[800px] p-12 mx-auto"
  >
    <h1 class="font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase">Ben Bleikamp</h1>
    <p class="font-light uppercase tracking-widest mb-12">
      Software designer & builder
    </p>
    <Shader />
    <div class="mt-12">
      <div class="uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold mb-6">Now</div>
      <div class="col-span-9 leading-relaxed mb-12">
        Currently building <a href="http://cased.com">Cased</a> in Mill Valley, California.
        When I'm not working, I'm riding gravel bikes, skiing, or trying to get in
        to woodworking.
      </div>
      <div class="uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold mb-6">Recently</div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 leading-relaxed mb-12">
        Spent a few years in Colorado for a few years. Before that, spent a
        decade in San Francisco working at start ups.
      </div>
      <div class="uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold mb-6">Work</div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 leading-relaxed mb-12">
        <p class="col-span-9 leading-relaxed">
          At Cased, we build tools that help developers work with
          infrastructure. We're backed by Founders Fund, Sancus, GTM Fund, and
          other investors who understand what we're trying to solve.
        </p>
        <p>
          I've spent 15 years designing and building software at small start ups
          and big companies. And I've had the opportunity to see small start ups
          become big companies.
        </p>
        <p>Previously:</p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <span class="whitespace-nowrap">Meta</span>
              <span
                class="flex-grow mx-2 overflow-hidden whitespace-nowrap text-neutral-300 dots-separator"
              ></span>
              <span class="whitespace-nowrap">2017-2018</span>
            </div>
            <div class="text-slate-500">Design Manager</div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <span class="whitespace-nowrap">GitHub</span>
              <span
                class="flex-grow mx-2 overflow-hidden whitespace-nowrap text-neutral-300 dots-separator"
              ></span>
              <span class="whitespace-nowrap">2011-2017</span>
            </div>
            <div class="text-slate-500">Head of Design, &c.</div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <span class="whitespace-nowrap">Yelp</span>
              <span
                class="flex-grow mx-2 overflow-hidden whitespace-nowrap text-neutral-300 dots-separator"
              ></span>
              <span class="whitespace-nowrap">2009-2011</span>
            </div>
            <div class="text-slate-500">Product Manager</div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <span class="whitespace-nowrap">Bleacher Report</span>
              <span
                class="flex-grow mx-2 overflow-hidden whitespace-nowrap text-neutral-300 dots-separator"
              ></span>
              <span class="whitespace-nowrap">2008-2009</span>
            </div>
            <div class="text-slate-500">Designer</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold mb-6">Say hi</div>
      <div class="col-span-9 leading-relaxed mb-12">
        Email me at ben@bleikamp.com
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .dots-separator {
    position: relative;
  }

  .dots-separator::after {
    content: "...................................................................................................................................................................................................................................";
    overflow: hidden;
    display: block;
  }
</style>
